Nearly a century after magic was recognized as a real form of technology, Miyuki Shiba begins her term at Magic High School. An honor student, she dreamed of enjoying school with her older brother Tatsuya, an irregular student. But a rift between the gifted Course 1 students and the inferior Course 2 students could stand in the way. This time, Miyuki is the star of the show!
(Source: Funimation)
Genjitsu Shugi Yuusha no Oukoku Saikenki

Suddenly summoned to a fantasy world and betrothed to the princess, Kazuya Souma is crowned the new king after providing the royal family with impressive advice. To rule the kingdom, he's taking the nontraditional (and very human) route of administrative reform. In a realm of dragons and elves, will this revolutionary's unique path prove effective?
(Source: Funimation)
Ashita, Watashi wa Dareka no Kanojo

"One time a week, I will be the girlfriend of [someone]." A bitter love story depicting the realities of love between female college students who earn money on behalf of her and men attracted by her. The first volume is a young office worker who rents the protagonist snow as a fake girlfriend, and draws a distorted love pattern of sota and snow. A substitute girl who plays the customer and the woman of their ideals to the end... Is the distance between two people's mind really close?
<i>Nominated for the Tsugimanga 2020 Award in the Web Manga Category.<i>
Akutou Ikka no Manamusume, Tenseisaki mo Otome Game no Gokudou Reijoudeshita.: Saijoukyuu Ranku no Akuyaku-sama, sono Dekiai wa Fuyoudesu! @COMIC

After her sudden death at the hands of an assassin, the former granddaughter of a yakuza boss reincarnates in an otome game as the heroine. The game is, of course, set in the time of early European mafia (but with magic), specifically a kingdom where the royal family is supported behind the scenes by five major gangsters!

A dangerous love game between a former yakuza heiress and her villain fianc begins!

(Source: TO Books, translated) (Source: TO Books, translated)
